snippet.title: Peter Wood
snippet.description:
Peter Wood crafts extraordinary entertainment for corporate events and private parties. His one-of-a-kind collection of impossibilities amazes audiences, mixed with hilarious comedy and unparalleled showmanship.

For more than two decades, Peter’s magical presentations have been enjoyed by top companies, including Frito-Lay, Microsoft, Lockheed Martin, USA Today, World Bank, and Adobe.  Government organizations, such as the Federal Bureau of Investigation, Naval Research Laboratory, United States Census Bureau, and the Federal Transit Administration also rely on his unique abilities.

When not performing, Peter’s specific skillset has led him to design and consult for film projects, theatrical productions, and his fellow performers.

He worked behind the scenes on the groundbreaking Penn & Teller Masterclass in Las Vegas, and his creations have appeared in several film festivals, as well as stages in Sweden, Brunei, New York, and at the Kennedy Center for the Performing Arts.
